Harris was convicted on Monday of 12 counts of indecent assault on victims as young as seven after a jury refused to believe his protestations of innocence during the eight-week trial.

The court heard that Harris, who faces jail on Friday, was a ‘Jekyll and Hyde’ predator who targeted youngsters and thought he was ‘above the law’.

